                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Linwood Seminary</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>Feby 9th 1866</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir-</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Will you be kind<lb/> enough on the receipt of this to<lb/> send\n                    <persName>Wm. H. Simons</persName>\n                <hi rend=\"sup\"><placeName>NY</placeName></hi> 50 “Select Sentences,„<lb/> enclosing\n                the Bill of them, having<lb/> just heard from my friend <persName>Mrs. M. L.<lb/>\n                    Samuel</persName>, of <placeName>Staten Island</placeName>, that <persName>Mrs.\n                    S.</persName><lb/> wishes that number sent to her, she<lb/> intending to\n                introduce them in her<lb/> school, I trust this will not be<lb/> too much\n                trouble.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">All the trouble you have to taken<lb/> for our school has failed, as\n                the only<lb/> two <sic>Isrealites</sic>, we had were not bright<lb/> enough to do us\n                credit, however<lb/> I still have <hi rend=\"underline\">Trust</hi> &amp; <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Faith</hi>, that</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ft8f19h/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
