                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ft8f19h/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p><hi rend=\"underline\">Our Father</hi>, will ever provide for<lb/> us that which <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">He</hi> in <hi rend=\"underline\">His</hi> wisdom,<lb/> knows is\n                for our good.</p>\n            <p>Do you not think it would be a<lb/> good plan to send one of the “Selected\n                Sen<lb/>tences” to each of the Jewish Schools, in<lb/>\n                <placeName>NY</placeName> as a sample, it might be beneficial<lb/> or to the\n                Principals of Sunday Schools,<lb/> in different States, I am anxious<lb/> to\n                liquidate my indebtedness to you<lb/> that you must excuse my troubling<lb/> you,\n                but as you have ever professed<lb/> yourself &amp; acted as a friend I claim<lb/>\n                the indulgence of one,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Ever respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">Truly yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">H. Emanuel</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>To</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>The</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>1227 Walnut St.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>Phila</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ft8f19h/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
